data.description: Welcome home to this traditional-southern-style home nestled in the River Vista Estates subdivision.  This home offers a spacious open floor plan and layout with 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a custom canyon kitchen with granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances, and a spacious master bedroom with fireplace and trey ceilings.  There are multiple large decks overlooking a private yard and an unfinished basement waiting for your creative ideas for entertainment and living space.  Living in the city of Ellenwood offers a perfect balance of southern living and is in close proximity to the dining, travel, and entertainment of the ATL.  Enjoy all the amenities without the hustle and make this home yours!
